\emdash \loch\f45  native on Snapdragon X, translated on Intel and AMD \hich\f45 \emdash \loch\f45  sharing nothing with the host machine.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af46\afs26 \ltrch\fcs0 \f46\fs26\kerning0\insrsid11555524 
