The fifth phase, estimated at six to twelve months, is product polish \hich\f46 \emdash \loch\f46 
 installer, configuration tools, documentation, support infrastructure, and the cross-partition input switching mechanism. This phase culminates in a public release.
\par \hich\af46\dbch\af31505\loch\f46 
The total timeline from phase one to phase five is approximately four to five years for a dedicated team of five to ten engineers, or longer for a smaller team. Working part-time alongside a four-year computer science degree, expect this to be a six-to-ei
\hich\af46\dbch\af31505\loch\f46 ght year project for the full vision, with intermediate milestones that produce real capability along the way.
